args.desc: Asset A must be less than Asset B

args.name: assetB
args.desc: Asset B

methods.name: calculateAssetBWithdrawOnLpDeposit
methods.desc: Calculates how much asset B will be taken from the smart contract on LP asset deposit

args.name: inAmount
args.desc: LP Asset amount in Base decimal representation..

args.name: assetBBalance
args.desc: Asset B balance. Variable ab, in base scale

args.name: liquidity
args.desc: Current liquidity. Variable L, in base scale

returns.desc: Amount of asset B to be given to the caller before fees. The result is in Base decimals (9)
